FOR AUTOSTART CHROMIUM ON PI
****************************

# Edit this file
sudo nano /home/pi/.config/lxsession/LXDE-pi/autostart

# And add this:
@xset s off
@xset -dpms
@xset s noblank
@chromium-browser --kiosk http://google.com/  # load chromium after boot and point to the localhost webserver in full screen mode